        "sender_full_name": "Stepan Nesterov",
        "timestamp": 1769643303
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It's a natural thing to try and get into mathlib and <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"464700\">@David Ang</span> was thinking about it but I don't know the status. He spoke about it at LT2025 IIRC</p>",
        "id": 570682806,
